====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[pass through]]; to [[travel]] [[through]]; to [[go]] [[through]]; or, to allow [[passage]]
#: {{zh-co|通心粉|macaroni|lit=pass-through heart pasta}}
#: {{zh-co|行不通|to be not feasible}}
#: {{zh-co|此 路 不通|No '''passing''' road.}}
#: {{zh-x|結束 了 沿線 八 個 縣 不 通 鐵路 的 歷史。|Ending the history of railroads not '''passing through''' these eight counties.}}
